are both coming in tomorrow.

97
00:05:29,890 --> 00:05:31,290
I can't move forward
with either until you sign off

98
00:05:31,358 --> 00:05:32,992
on what I worked through lunch to finish.

99
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:35,795
I'm sorry. I had a long lunch,
went for a swim.

100
00:05:35,863 --> 00:05:37,630
Come back in an hour. I'm taking a nap.

101
00:05:42,069 --> 00:05:44,670
It's a business of sadists and masochists,

102
00:05:44,738 --> 00:05:46,472
and you know which one you are.

103
